  "summary": {
    "as": "Reported to House",
    "asOf": "2024-07-05",
    "date": "2024-08-05T19:28:24Z",
    "text": "Combating the Lies of Authoritarians in School Systems Act or the CLASS Act\n\nThis bill requires public elementary and secondary schools, as a condition of receiving federal elementary and secondary education funds,\u00a0to disclose to the Department of Education any funding from\u00a0or contracts with a foreign source that exceed $10,000."
